{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"249eff66c9","title":"云南大学右派的反动言论（4）","origin":"《云南省高等学校右派分子反动言论选集》(中国共产党云南省高等学校委员会办公室编印，1957.8.15)，内部资料。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"785a3a56b0","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"249eff66c9"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19ed423a88","name":"钱志诚"},{"id":"646a52e3a7","name":"王文璐"},{"id":"9163c0a865","name":"云南大学教师"},{"id":"9f78ca9746","name":"蒙绍养"},{"id":"f727dfccca","name":"黄震"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"dd5c41ed98","type":"title","text":"云南大学右派的反动言论 （4）","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"1112f7820f","type":"authors","text":"云南大学教师钱志诚蒙绍养王文璐黄震","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"097748eb2b","type":"paragraph","text":"钱志诚(云南大学体育教研组讲师)说：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"6a809fe26e","type":"subtitle","text":"党委会是衙门","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"6ee53574dc","type":"paragraph","text":"党委会是衙门、宗派、阎罗殿。党员是老爷，将来一定要成为东霸天，西霸天。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"fadf8e3f2d","type":"paragraph","text":"党有唯党员论。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"1205b24489","type":"paragraph","text":"党委包办一切，决定一切。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"fbfcf7f61f","type":"subtitle","text":"社会主义制度一切都不民主","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"e0b58bb896","type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义制度下一切都不民主，现在不如过去。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"239b30fae8","type":"paragraph","text":"“民主”是走过场而已。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"a15ecfb463","type":"paragraph","text":"选举不要党提名。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"cc1bf2301c","type":"paragraph","text":"“党天下”的说法符合事实。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"52ca5f67c5","type":"subtitle","text":"人事制度邪气上升","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"a945d4236f","type":"paragraph","text":"有了人事制度就会邪气上升，有才的人发挥不出。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"1b244d75a9","type":"paragraph","text":"升级的标准就是党员，不管狗屎、牛屎，能不能作，都弄成科长。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"1cc2f3b756","type":"paragraph","text":"名誉上加点薪，实际上生活水平并没有提高，还不如过去。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"c43c0233e5","type":"paragraph","text":"蒙绍养（云南大学助教）说：","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"3637e2586a","type":"subtitle","text":"共产党是石头上的红布","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"a7aa39e3c3","type":"paragraph","text":"共产党是石头上的红布。那里有工人阶级？工人阶级是抽象的。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"3c2bccc072","type":"paragraph","text":"要求入党入团的人都是有个人企图的。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"d418ecd8dc","type":"subtitle","text":"搞政治的人就是想做官","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"4cfb064c7b","type":"paragraph","text":"搞政治的人就是想做官，为的是名、利。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"e41a7b375f","type":"paragraph","text":"国民党有一套，共产党的一套就是马列主义。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"2f1216c76c","type":"subtitle","text":"现在还不如解放前","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"524f162898","type":"paragraph","text":"三定政策搞糟了，统购统销也搞糟了。农民一年吃十两油，还不如解放前。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"e5a8ba50bb","type":"paragraph","text":"报纸天天吹大丰收，为什么广西还饿死人？","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"85096ccd79","type":"subtitle","text":"反革命是分析出来的","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"0e018afea0","type":"paragraph","text":"分析分析就会分析出一个胡风反革命集团来。分析分析就分析出一个反革命来。就肃反有成绩，是因为镇反没有杀着你家的人。","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"39ba818686","type":"subtitle","text":"蒋介石当部长，小特务倒霉","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"45984ae880","type":"paragraph","text":"蒋介石回来可当部长，倒霉的是小特务。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"912efb0ab1","type":"paragraph","text":"葛佩琦的言论是爱国的逆耳忠言。","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"b82efa7a15","type":"paragraph","text":"王文璐(云南大学化学系助教)说：","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"6fc956fe48","type":"subtitle","text":"任何党派都是宗派集团","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"6c4af7426a","type":"paragraph","text":"无论什么党派都是宗派集团，官官相顾，共产党与国民党一样。","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"9e501bf22e","type":"paragraph","text":"黄震(云南大学工会秘书)说：","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"d7b8d68567","type":"subtitle","text":"党团委不懂文艺，但又硬把持文艺领导岗位","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"b8972da4c0","type":"paragraph","text":"在鸣放中提出要办一个刊物与校刊争鸣；这个刊物不受党团干预，可以凭“正义感来独立负责”。他在一次座谈会上说：“云南省文艺界的这些领导，只是领导政治，不懂文学艺术。而这方面有才学的人未能得到重视。党团委这些同志是不懂文艺的。党就是让一些不懂文艺的人硬把持着文艺领导岗位。这是全国性的问题”。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"86a59f41b1","type":"subtitle","text":"社会主义现实主义是庸俗社会学","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"fff7a516b4","type":"paragraph","text":"“百家争鸣，百花齐放了，其他非社会主义现实主义的创作方法也可写出有利于人民的作品。过去按社会主义现实主义的创作方法，就造成了我国文学艺术的一般化、公式化、概念化，这是教条主义的罪过，是庸俗社会学”。在鸣放前，他曾企图夺取校刊“山茶”文艺栏的编辑权，要求学校交给他所组织的一伙人去办，学校无权修改稿件。","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"80eaac16f8","type":"paragraph","text":"他仿照“草木篇”写了“树”、“乌鸦”等诗攻击今天的社会主义制度和党的领导，文如下：","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"c8e5cb45c9","type":"subtitle","text":"树","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"c033a951cb","type":"paragraph","text":"古老而倔强的树","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"2d482b87d5","type":"paragraph","text":"曾有过茂盛的枝叶","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"24a090a37a","type":"paragraph","text":"却被横暴的雷电摧光折尽","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"654585e368","type":"paragraph","text":"但是","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"7473402a97","type":"paragraph","text":"它的干仍然深深地连着土地","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"7638ccd978","type":"paragraph","text":"那悄悄地冒着的新芽","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"ef34c50393","type":"paragraph","text":"又预示着在开始它生命的青春","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"2e51f7e3f7","type":"subtitle","text":"乌鸦","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"84716e9300","type":"paragraph","text":"只有一种颜色","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"1178d95d89","type":"paragraph","text":"——黑，黑，黑。","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"25b10a8620","type":"paragraph","text":"只会一个调门，","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"c3c1f88c8e","type":"paragraph","text":"——吖，吖，吖。","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"a4efe32f38","type":"paragraph","text":"整天价喋喋不休。","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"},{"id":"e0a81d6ebe","type":"paragraph","text":"似乎不知道自己的短处是啥。","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9"}],"page":{"id":"4d8e22505a","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"249eff66c9","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}